data.description: Step into your new haven – a captivating quad-level home boasting 3 bedrooms with potential for a 4th, and 2.5 bathrooms, nestled on an expansive corner lot that gracefully backs onto serene woods. This residence offers an array of modern comforts, including a recently installed furnace (2020) and hot water tank (2020), ensuring a cozy atmosphere year-round. The kitchen showcases the latest in culinary convenience with newer stainless steel appliances, enhancing the heart of your home. Unwind in the sunroom, or step outside to your expansive deck, complete with a manually retractable awning – the perfect setting for summer days of leisure or entertaining. This residence seamlessly marries style and functionality, promising a delightful living experience for years to come. Welcome home. Conveniently located near expressways and shopping. BATVAI.
